## Credits / Prior Work
This project builds on the **CosmicWatch Desktop Muon Detector (v2)** by Spencer N. Axani et al.  
Source: https://github.com/spenceraxani/CosmicWatch-Desktop-Muon-Detector-v2  
I referenced their detector design/materials and library patterns while writing my firmware.
